<v-container fluid>
  <v-slide-y-transition mode="out-in">
    <v-layout column align-center>
      <v-card
      height="200"
      width="400"
      >
      <v-form v-model="valid">
        <v-text-field
          v-model="title"
          :rules="titleRules"
          label="Title"
          required
        ></v-text-field>
        <v-textarea
          v-model="content"
          label="Content"
          :rules="contentRules"
          rows="3"
          required
        ></v-textarea>
        <v-btn
          v-on:click.prevent="createNote()"
          absolute
          dark
          fab
          bottom
          right
          color="red"
          small
        >
          <v-icon>add</v-icon>
        </v-btn>
      </v-form>
      </v-card>
    </v-layout>
  </v-slide-y-transition>
</v-container>
